name: User Manual Concept
description:
This is a quick prototype of a user manual in the form of a mobile app. It is a manual about how to connect a guitar to a normal hifi system at home using a specific cable.


I made use of the Material 3 Design Kit and the Material Theme Builder for a custom color theme.


This file is in Dutch. My only reason for sharing this on the community is to help someone learn Figma, so I don't expect anyone to see or be interested in this. But if I'm wrong and someone is somehow actually interested, I can translate this file to English. Just ask :)
